01:26:20.280 --> 01:26:22.510
&gt;&gt; Devapriya Nayak:
So, it goes like this.

01:26:22.510 --> 01:26:34.620
[ Humming and Drum Beating ]

01:26:34.620 --> 01:26:35.920
&gt;&gt; Yasmeen Khan: OK.

01:26:35.920 --> 01:26:39.610
As you can see the significance
with the elephant walk.

01:26:39.610 --> 01:26:40.910
&gt;&gt; Yasmeen Khan: It
